high_descs: Go left, then right on passing the shelves, and face the shelf.
Take a tomato from the shelf.
Turn around and walk to the microwave on your right.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
Walk to the sidetable to your left.
Take a tomato from the table.
Return to the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Move two tomatoes, from a shelf and from a round table, to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left to walk down the passage and head to the shelf on the right.
Pick up the tomato from the shelf.
Turn left to reach the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
Turn left to reach the sidetable.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Turn around to reach the microwave on the left.
Put the tomato behind the other tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put two Tomato in the Microwave.

high_descs: Turn left & walk a few steps then turn right and walk a few steps and turn right to stand facing the wooden shelf.
Pick up the tomato from the lower rack.
Turn around and make your way to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the tomato in it.
Close the sidetable and make your way to the sofa set.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Turn around and make your way to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the tomato in it and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put all the tomatoes into the microwave.
